cf.DimensionCoordinate.size¶

DimensionCoordinate.size¶

The number of elements in the data array.

See also

data, hasdata, ndim, shape

Examples: 
>>> f.shape
(73, 96)
>>> f.size
7008

>>> f.shape
()
>>> f.ndim
0
>>> f.size
1

>>> f.shape
(1, 1, 1)
>>> f.ndim
3
>>> f.size
1

>>> f.hasdata
True
>>> f.size == reduce(lambda x, y: x*y, f.shape, 1)
True
